						<div class="postbody">There are general map editors around, actually, but not much people ever heard of them.
<br />
<br />For me, making a custom level editor (if necessary for a project) takes about one day, or less, if one of old editors is similar enough to be easily modified. Making plugins or converters for a general map editor would take probably the same amount of time.</div>

					
